<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 09 at 3:29AM EDT  by NWS Chicago</headline>
<description>...Locally Slippery Conditions this Morning...
Light snow early this morning with temperatures near freezing has
resulted in a thin layer of accumulation on some area roadways.
Locally slippery conditions are possible through daybreak,
especially on elevated surfaces such as bridges and overpasses. Be
prepared for varying road conditions if traveling this morning.</description>
